data.description: Seller offering $10,000 flooring allowance. Brick, ranch style home with full finished basement, attached one car garage plus detached one car garage off alley.  Priced so you can upgrade and make it your own and build equity with paint and floor coverings and your personal touches.  Main floor laundry.  All appliances are included, also extra kitchenette in basement.  Central AC, humidifier + attic fan.  Fenced back yard, patio, alley access.  Detached garage makes great workshop. New roof 2021 & HVAC in 2015.
